# Testing
- vitest. Unit-test all deterministic logic with fakes for db/MCP/LLM.
- Write INVARIANT TESTS first for each milestone (esp. invariant 1: a heal carrying an assertion diff must fail).
- The eval harness replays recorded trajectories against an agent/prompt version and scores it; a regression
  vs the golden baseline fails the run. Golden cases live in fixtures/ and are committed.
- No test depends on a live external service; MCP and the model gateway are faked in CI.
